  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover many strange and intriguing ideas in this abstract puzzle/action/adventure game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ rooms to uncover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique unlockable abilities that afford further exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic soundtrack that changes in each room</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome challenging obstacles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharpen your reflexes to slip past dangerous hazards. Collect as many flashing<i> alloy</i> as you can, but be sure to make it back to the checkpoint in one piece!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455110/extras/c79fb198212abe71bdea8eb399ad61da.poster.avif?t=1752719156\" width=596 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455110/extras/c79fb198212abe71bdea8eb399ad61da.webm?t=1752719156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455110/extras/c79fb198212abe71bdea8eb399ad61da.mp4?t=1752719156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Distort space</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock various abilities that let you bend the walls around you to reach otherwise inaccessible places...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455110/extras/13e288341dc6c0809d99aa101e3ed69d.poster.avif?t=1752719156\" width=596 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4551